USAGE NOTICE

This software is designed for educational and research purposes. When using
this software:

1. Respect website terms of service and robots.txt files
2. Use appropriate delays between requests to avoid overloading servers
3. Cite data sources appropriately in any publications or reports
4. Verify critical findings through manual review
5. Do not use for commercial purposes without proper authorization

The data collected by this software comes from publicly available government
websites and should be attributed to the respective state education departments.
